# Lead delivery via Resend (https://resend.com). Copy to `.env.local`.
# `.env.local` is gitignored — NEVER commit real keys.

# Get a key at https://resend.com (Settings -> API Keys). A restricted
# "sending only" key is fine and recommended.
RESEND_API_KEY=

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTION A — works today, no DNS setup (sandbox sender)
# Leads land in the Resend account owner's inbox. Until you verify a
# custom domain, Resend ONLY allows this sender, and only to the owner.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
RESEND_FROM="Manaseerz Electric <onboarding@resend.dev>"
CONTACT_EMAIL="manaseerzelectrical@gmail.com"

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTION B — fully branded (recommended once domain is verified)
# 1. https://resend.com/domains -> Add Domain -> "manaseerz.com"
# 2. Add the 3 DNS records Resend shows you (SPF + DKIM + tracking) at
#    your DNS provider, wait for "Verified".
# 3. Swap to these values:
#      RESEND_FROM="Manaseerz Electric <leads@manaseerz.com>"
#      CONTACT_EMAIL="info@manaseerz.com"
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
